WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
URUGUAY.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY IN PROGRESS UNTIL 16 OCT
   BY M/V RAMFORM VANGUARD TOWING
   12 7000 METER LONG CABLES ALONG TRACKLINES BETWEEN:
   A. 35-48.07S 053-04.48W AND 35-10.07S 052-26.43W
   B. 35-13.15S 052-25.40W AND 35-53.63S 053-05.98W
   NINE MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 17 OCT 13.
